---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contribute - Dhwani">
  <main>
    <article class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 max-w-[1100px] mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-[clamp(2.5rem,7vw,4.5rem)] font-semibold leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.025em] text-ink mb-10 md:mb-12">
        Contribute to Dhwani
      </h1>

      <div class="prose-content space-y-7 md:space-y-8">
        <p class="font-serif-body text-[1rem] md:text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.75] md:leading-[1.85] text-ink-light font-light">
          Help us preserve and share India's literary heritage. Whether you know of overlooked works, can provide translations, or want to contribute historical context, your knowledge helps make this archive more complete.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-[1.65rem] md:text-[2rem] font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink mt-12 md:mt-14 mb-6 md:mb-7">
          Ways to Contribute
        </h2>

        <h3 class="font-serif text-[1.35rem] md:text-[1.5rem] font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink mt-10 mb-4">
          Suggest New Works
        </h3>

        <p class="font-serif-body text-[1rem] md:text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.75] md:leading-[1.85] text-ink-light font-light">
          Know of a public domain work that should be included? Share it with us. We're especially interested in lesser-known regional literature, translations, and historical texts.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-2.5 md:space-y-3 font-serif-body text-[0.95rem] md:text-[1.05rem] leading-[1.7] md:leading-[1.8] text-ink-light font-light">
          <li>Work must be in the public domain or available under an open license</li>
          <li>Include author, title, publication year, and source link</li>
          <li>Provide brief context about the work's significance</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-serif text-[1.35rem] md:text-[1.5rem] font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink mt-10 mb-4">
          Add Context & Analysis
        </h3>

        <p class="font-serif-body text-[1rem] md:text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.75] md:leading-[1.85] text-ink-light font-light">
          Help readers understand the historical and cultural significance of works. Write introductions, provide biographical information about authors, or explain literary movements.
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-serif text-[1.35rem] md:text-[1.5rem] font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink mt-10 mb-4">
          Fix Errors & Improve Metadata
        </h3>

        <p class="font-serif-body text-[1rem] md:text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.75] md:leading-[1.85] text-ink-light font-light">
          Spotted an error in dates, author names, or descriptions? Help us maintain accuracy by reporting corrections.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-[1.65rem] md:text-[2rem] font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink mt-12 md:mt-14 mb-6 md:mb-7">
          Get in Touch
        </h2>

        <p class="font-serif-body text-[1rem] md:text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.75] md:leading-[1.85] text-ink-light font-light">
          Send your contributions, suggestions, or questions to <a href="mailto:hello@dhwani.org" class="text-accent underline">hello@dhwani.org</a>
        </p>

        <p class="font-serif-body text-[1rem] md:text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.75] md:leading-[1.85] text-ink-light font-light">
          Dhwani is an open-source project. You can also contribute code, design improvements, or help with infrastructure on our GitHub repository.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-12 md:mt-14 pt-7 md:pt-8 border-t border-line">
          <p class="font-serif-body text-sm text-ink-lighter font-light">
            Every contribution, no matter how small, helps preserve and share India's literary heritage for future generations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
